# Privacy Policy

**Last Updated:** {{ "now().strftime('%B %d, %Y')" }}

This Privacy Policy describes how {{ project_name }} ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares your personal information when you use our services.

## 1. Information We Collect

### 1.1 Information You Provide

We collect information you provide directly to us:

- **Account Information**: Name, email address, password
{% if saas_tenancy_model == "b2b-teams" %}
- **Organization Information**: Company name, team member details, billing information
{% endif %}
- **Profile Information**: Optional profile details, preferences, settings
- **Payment Information**: Billing address, payment method details (processed by {{ saas_billing_provider | title }})
- **Communications**: Messages, support requests, feedback

### 1.2 Information Collected Automatically

When you use our services, we automatically collect:

- **Usage Data**: Pages visited, features used, time spent, clicks
- **Device Information**: Browser type, operating system, device identifiers
- **Location Data**: Approximate location based on IP address
{% if saas_analytics == "posthog" %}
- **Analytics**: Session recordings, feature usage, funnel analysis (PostHog)
{% elif saas_analytics == "amplitude" %}
- **Analytics**: Event tracking, user cohorts, behavior flows (Amplitude)
{% endif %}
- **Cookies**: See our Cookie Policy section below

### 1.3 Information from Third Parties

{% if saas_auth_provider == "clerk" %}
- **Authentication**: Profile information from social login providers (Google, GitHub, etc.) via Clerk
{% elif saas_auth_provider == "authjs" %}
- **Authentication**: Profile information from OAuth providers you connect
{% endif %}
{% if saas_enterprise_bridge == "workos" %}
